# Platform Module

## Module Purpose and Responsibilities

The Platform module is the portability seam of PigeonLib. It provides concrete implementations of every OS- and GPU-dependent operation so that all other engine modules can be written against stable abstract interfaces in `Pigeon/Core/` and `Pigeon/Renderer/`.

The module has two sub-trees that are mutually exclusive at compile time:

- **`Platform/Windows/`** — Win32 window management and raw-input polling, compiled into every non-testing build on Windows.
- **`Platform/Testing/`** — in-process stubs compiled only under the `Testing` configuration (`TESTS_ENABLED` defined). They replace every OS/GPU call with a no-op or a deterministic in-memory implementation so that unit tests run without a display device.

The module also owns the `TESTS_ENABLED`-gated factory functions (`Window::Create`, `PlatformInput::s_Instance`) that select between the two sub-trees at link time.

---

## Source Files

| File | Sub-tree | Role |
|---|---|---|
| `Platform/Windows/WindowsWindow.h/.cpp` | Windows | Win32 window, message loop, event dispatch |
| `Platform/Windows/WindowsInput.h/.cpp` | Windows | Raw-input polling via `GetAsyncKeyState`, code mapping |
| `Platform/Windows/WindowsInputKeyCodeMapping.h` | Windows | `WIN_PG_*` constants mapping Win32 VK codes to engine key codes |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingWindow.h/.cpp` | Testing | Stub window — no OS calls; exposes `TESTING_TriggerEvent` |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingInput.h/.cpp` | Testing | Stub input — driven by public `TESTING_*` data members |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingContext.h/.cpp` | Testing | Stub graphics context — all methods are no-ops, width/height always 0 |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingRendererAPI.h/.cpp` | Testing | Stub renderer API — clears `TestingHelper` tracking vectors on `Begin()` |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingBuffer.h/.cpp` | Testing | Stub vertex/index buffers — record calls in `TestingHelper` |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingShader.h/.cpp` | Testing | Stub shader — all uniform uploads are no-ops |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingTexture.h/.cpp` | Testing | Stub textures — dimensions driven by static `s_ExpectedWidth/Height` |
| `Platform/Testing/TestingHelper.h/.cpp` | Testing | Singleton observation log used by unit-test assertions |

